info.description:
The services given in this document for creating booking on third party systems. The bookings once created will be received on the sun telematics platform.


  Explanation of the Booking Api keys is mentioned below.

            "key": {This will be a secured key shared by Sun Telematics to  BTR. This key will be passed as the Authorization header while calling this api},

            "vendor_id": {This is a partner code, mutually decided between BTR and SunTelematics, Will be same for all the Bookings}

            "partner_name": { Will always be  BTR , it will use by the sun telematics to identify that the booking is from the BTR }

            "order_reference_number": {This will be the Booking reference id Of partner, always unique for each Booking"}

            "passenger_name": {Name of the passenger travelling}

            "passenger_email": {Email id of the passenger}

            "passenger_phone_number": {Phonenumber of the passenger}

            "source_name": { pickup address of the passenger}

            "source_city": { pickup city of the passenger }

            "source_latitude": {28.5647}

            "source_longitude": {77.1949}

            "start_time": {2019-10-14 12:30:00}

            "destination_name": {sector-62 noida, India}

            "destination_city": {Noida}

            "destination_latitude": {30.7333}

            "destination_longitude": {76.7794}

            "total_distance": {This will be the total distance calculated from the source Lat/Long to the destination Lat/Long, using google's/map my india distance api}

            "total_fare": {Total fare calculated as per the TnC of the  team}

            "verification_code": {This token will be used by the driver to identify the passenger at the time of boarding}

            "flight_number": { (Optional / partner can send as 'NA')}

            "is_toll_included": true,

            "is_parking_included": true,

            "extra_km_fare" : 20.38,

            "wait_time": 30,

            "is_part_payment" : {true/false, if true it means the user has done part payment for this Booking, and the remaining amount to be collected from Sun Telematics as it's mentioned in the key "amount_to_be_collected}

            "vehicle_type": {sedan/hatchback/suv}

            "service_type" : { ["airport", "outstation", "package"]  as Trip type}

            "is_airport_pickup" : true

            "is_airport_drop" : false

            "amount_to_be_collected": {This is as per the key "is_part_payment}

            "placard_subtitle": {(Optional / partner can send as 'NA')}

            "end_time": {Expected end time of trip}

 "This is only for the explanation of the keys/value of API"
